tool_description: API to detect disposable domains to help companies reject disposable emails which has created LEAD GENERATION nightmare in recent times,detect fake email address, Generate common domain,unique domain names, generate custom email addresses using domain name, check whois of a domain and alot more.
title: Anything Domain

api_list.name: Domain Status
api_list.description: Check the status or availability of a domain before purchase. Returns TRUE if domain is available for purchase else FALSE.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://anything-domain.p.rapidapi.com/domain-status/{id}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "anything-domain.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
